Package: lexis
Title: English Psycholinguistic Norms in a Unified Tidy Resource
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jay", "Timm", email = "jay.timm01@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Compiles 13 English psycholinguistic norming datasets (age of acquisition,
    concreteness, valence/arousal/dominance, imageability, body-object interaction,
    humor, socialness, sensory experience, Lancaster sensorimotor norms, word prevalence,
    lexical decision times, verbs-in-space, and gender connotation) together with
    Wordset definition counts, and GloVe word embeddings
    into a single tidy resource. Provides utility functions for lookup, search,
    filtering, definition retrieval, embedding-based neighbor search, and stimulus
    matching.
